show_name: Bleach the Movie: Memories of Nobody
other_title: 劇場版BLEACH [ブリーチ] MEMORIES OF NOBODY (Japanese)
plot: In Karakura Town, there has been a sudden outbreak of unidentifiable spirits called "blanks" (vacant souls) while in the skies of Soul Society, the real world has been reflected. A mysterious female shinigami called Senna has appeared before Ichigo along with a man named Ganryu, leading a group called the "Dark Ones".
ending_theme: "Sen no Yoru wo Koete" by Aqua Timez
